MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 1 : Increases Pistol damage based on Outlander Lab Rating.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 1 : Increases Pistol damage based on Outlander Lab Rating.

MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 2 : Reduces the Energy cost of Anti Material Charge by 15.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 2 : Reduces the Energy cost of Anti Material Charge by 15.

MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 3 : Increases the critical hit chance of Pistols based on Outlander Lab Rating.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 3 : Increases the critical hit chance of Pistols based on Outlander Lab Rating.

MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 4 : Knock, Knock! :  Destroying a Wall causes a wave of Energy to flow outwards from the wreckage, damaging enemies.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 4 : Knock, Knock! :  Destroying a Wall causes a wave of Energy to flow outwards from the wreckage, damaging enemies.

MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 5 : Trigger Happy : Killing an enemy with Anti Material Charge resets it's cooldown. Can only trigger once every 10 seconds.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 5 : Trigger Happy : Killing an enemy with Anti Material Charge resets it's cooldown. Can only trigger once every 10 seconds.
